.square#board
  #instructions
    The goal is to add one ingredient of each color,
    = succeed ", " do
      %span{:style => "color:orange;font-weight:bold"} orange
    = succeed ", " do
      %span{:style => "color:yellow;font-weight:bold"} yellow
    %span{:style => "color:green;font-weight:bold"} green
    and
    = succeed " to" do
      %span{:style => "color:pink;font-weight:bold"} pink
    the empty box on the left. Click on two of the same ingredient, and you lose a cupcake (which is the same as losing a life, amirite?). Lose three (3) lives and the game is lost. Have fun!





